    <has_dmc>No</has_dmc>
  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Bevacizumab might influence the dynamic vessel function after being administered
      intravenously.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      By monitoring different vessel and circulation parameters (e.g. dynamic retinal vessel
      analyzer) the study will clarify the potential hemodynamic effects of bevacizumab.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
